functions snake_case

methods snake_case

variables snake_case

member variables snake_case

types PascalCase

namespaces PascalCase

enum names PascalCase

enum values MACRO_CASE

// code conventions

always use struct over class unless it has to many private members

every llvm value in struct|class should have the prefix llvm_

enums should be enum class

everything that wont be modified should be declared 'const'

minimize the use of exceptions. always use the version without exceptions in std lib
